Want to take your next laser appointment further? Try combining our two newest modalities for the ultimate in skin rejuvenation. 

Here’s how it works: 

MOXI uses non-ablative laser energy to improve texture, early signs of aging, and sun damage ☀️

BBL HEROic targets sun damage, redness, and pigmentation, while stimulating collagen production deep within the skin 💥

When you combine these two powerhouse treatments you can effectively target multiple skin concerns in one appointment. So you’re receiving maximum benefits with minimum downtime!
